 chocolate. Very sweet, polished tannins that sustain clean, highly elegant black berries."},{"id":"fr_FR","ocurrence":0,"type":"STRING","value":"Robe rouge cardinal foncé très couverte, largement violacée sur les bords. Intense et subtil, élégant et très complexe. Touches épicées de clou de girofle, poivre noir et bâton de réglisse. Plantes aromatiques, ciste et thym sur fond minéral et fruits rouges noirs très mûrs, comme la mûre, griotte, fraise et cerise. Tons épicés, entre minéraux d'encre de Chine et chocolat. Tanins très doux et polis sur un fruit noir bien marqué et très élégant."}]}]},{"id":"GestionComprasStock","type":"GROUPING","children":[{"id":"Calificacion1","type":"STRING","value":"CL"},{"id":"Calificacion2","type":"STRING","value":"A"},{"id":"Calificacion4","type":"STRING","value":"3N"},{"id":"Calificacion5","type":"STRING","value":"VV"},{"id":"TipoDeGestion","type":"STRING","value":"16"}]},{"id":"DimensionesYPeso","type":"GROUPING","children":[{"id":"UOM!Dimensiones!Unidad","type":"LOOKUP_TABLE","featureGroupID":"204","id_Ext":"347186090","value":"cm"},{"id":"UOM!PesoBruto!Unidad","type":"LOOKUP_TABLE","featureGroupID":"206","id_Ext":"347187090","value":"g"},{"id":"UOM!VolumenContenidoNeto!VolumenContenidoNeto","type":"NUMBER","value":"0.0"},{"id":"UOM!VolumenContenidoNeto!Unidad","type":"LOOKUP_TABLE","featureGroupID":"213","id_Ext":"347188090","value":"ml"},{"id":"PUM","type":"GROUPING","children":[{"id":"EnlacePUM","type":"LOOKUP_TABLE","featureGroupID":"2530","id_Ext":"20552573090","value":"005"},{"id":"CantidadProducto","type":"NUMBER","value":"75.0"},{"id":"UnidadesProducto","type":"STRING","value":"001"}]}]},{"id":"ColoresYTallas","type":"GROUPING","children":[{"id":"ColorFabricante","type":"STRING","value":"CRIANZA"},{"id":"TamanoHorma","type":"STRING","value":"D.O RIBERA DUER"},{"id":"Dibujo","type":"STRING","value":"BOTELLA   75CL"}]},{"id":"Variantes","type":"GROUPING","children":[{"id":"CodigoVarianteWeb","type":"STRING","value":"A139594